title: The Throne of Clay T1-T5 (2006-2012)  (Dragonz K)cbr
description:
France, 1418. The country is embroiled in a bloody civil war. The king, Charles VI., in the grip of madness, is unable to assert his authority and the fight over the succession of the kingdom is getting ever more bitter and vicious. In the midst of this chaos the English invade the Normandy, conquering one keep after another. The hundred year war flares up again, and the fate of France seems to be sealed ...

enjoy
